Title: 'Searching for homeland '
DateModified: '2019-03-05'
DatePublished: '2019-03-05'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/searching-for-homeland
SetInCountry: Lebanon
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Radwa Abdullatif
AuthorCountry: Egypt
Text: The story is about the refugees and their suffering to find a new homeland .
  They meanly live now in camps across borders in Lebanon Jordan and Iraq. Others
  are stucked in Greece Italy German and Bangladesh. But Lebanon is hosting the oldest
  refugees camp in the modern world which is called Ein  El Helwa . The story here
  is not about people but it is about culture places and coping the homland features
  to another land.
